# 33  Logger status monitoring

#### 33 Logger status monitoring

The Status functions are available as Windows PlugIn too.

The Status node is very useful to monitor the overall healthstatus of your logger. Critical process
and overall CPU and RAM usage can be effectifly monitored. When you use these chanels for
limit monitoring or triggerer events for notification e.g. over the IoT communication to your
mobile display and IPEcloud - fleet managemetn system. The following 3 channels are availabel
by default.
